_sText:
Quick Gun-Game map series.

GG_01 is the first map in my quick-map-making series.

The goal of this series is to produce as many completed maps as possible, mainly for experience.

The best will be re-textured, re-built and re-released.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

Description: A small, 2 leveled map that has an interesting feel due to the curved geometry.

Theme: Curves and Arches

Size: Small

Max Players: 44

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

At 6.3MB .bz2 is recommended.

Please tell me what you think.
